<h1 class="cover-heading">Akagoria, the revenge of Kalista</h1>
<p class="lead">Long ago, you were the greatest evil sorceress. But they defeated you, they forgot about you and now, they laugh at you. Find your power back!</p>

<p class="text-justify">Akagoria is a single-player <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Role-playing_video_game">role-playing game</a> in an <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_world">open world</a> with a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Top-down_perspective">top-down view</a>.</p>

<p class="text-justify">After a very long sleep, Kalista the sorceress starts a long journey to get her lost powers back. The world of Akagoria has changed, it is now a peaceful place where people only want to live a pleasant life. Kalista will have to go throught this unknown environment and accomplish a long quest with many surprises.</p>

